GLOBAL GAP YEAR
Gap Year Programs 











 Global Gap YearThis unparalleled adventure is TBB's signature program. You'll live, explore, and learn in six countries with friends who'll be with you for life. This is the ultimate gap year program if you want to make the most of your gap year and learn to create meaningful change in the world.  




  





Your TBB Gap Year Awaits! Are You Ready?Learn more about our industry leading gap year programs or apply now!Request Free InformationApply Now 




 Food Systems, Public Health, & the EnvironmentIt takes holistic knowledge and experience to resolve global issues. This program explores how sustainable practices can protect food and the environment, how education can truly empower, and how public health is the foundation for development.  




 


 


Program Details



Application Due: July 31, 2017
Program Length: 7 Months
Tuition: $31,000
Airfare: $5,000 (costs may vary)
Dates: Sept 11, ’17 – Mar 25, ’18
Group Size: 18 students & 3 Program Leaders




Watch an Alumni InterviewSee Reviews on GoOverseas.com 










 


 


